About:
Compendium is not a "best of" collection of songs. Compendium is, instead, a collection of important songs. Music that helps us all understand who Blue Stone is. Helps us better value their history, foundation and beginnings and takes us by the hand through each step of their progress. It's so much more than a best of album. Listen closely, this is your masters course in understanding the passion, dedication and obsession with perfection that is Blue Stone
